title: Recaptcha code incorrect
body: Im trying to log in on my computer to the forums and it keeps saying recaptcha code incorrect but it doesnt even show the captcha on multiple web browsers.

replies.body: There could be a few reasons for this, such browser extensions causing problems or a cache issue.  If running Incognito fixes this, then it may be necessary to [clean your cache and cookies ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)to resolve this.  Hope that helps!
